[0.000, "o", "\r\nPublish targets:\r\n  baseline_cast: site/videos/hello.cast\r\n  timeline: site/videos/hello.timeline.jsonl\r\n  recording_fingerprint: site/videos/hello.recording.json\r\n  voiceover: website/static/audio/casts/hello.mp3\r\n  audio_metadata: website/static/audio/casts/hello.json\r\n  retimed_cast: site/videos/hello.retimed.cast\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nPipeline:\r\n  1. record (compile): record a fast terminal baseline and timeline sidecar\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  2. audio_generate (compile): generate or reuse cached TTS fragments for each beat\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  3. audio_publish (link): concatenate voiceover and write audio timing metadata\r\n  4. retime (optimize): create the watchable cast using terminal and audio timing\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  5. publish_surface (link): embed the finished recording in the selected publish surface\r\n  6. align_check (validate): verify visible captions and commands still match the script\r\n\r\nNo commands were run.\r\n"]
[0.048, "o", "\r\n"]
